name: Freq.Trigger - PLAY your music (Canceled)
blurb: Freq.Trigger - a 2D physics-based shooter modified by music. Music changes everything and every song equals a unique gaming experience.

rewards.reward: The \u201cPositive\u201d tier - A big thank you and your name in lights on the \u2018Backers\u2019 page of our website // exclusive access to the \u2018Backers Lounge\u2019 - a special, private section in our forums. // A \u2018Backers\u2019 medal for your profile page on the website, plus a warm, fuzzy feeling for helping us out.  :-)

The \u201cBunch of Fives\u201d tier - All previous rewards + a free copy of the game (we aim to deliver this to you as a digital download before general release!) // + 5 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades).  Great!
The \u201cBinary\u201d tier - all previous rewards + a selection of digital artwork from the game for your Facebook page or blog // + 10 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades). Awesome!
The \u201cNatural 20\u201d tier - all previous rewards + an extra copy of the game for a friend! (aren't you nice!) // + 23 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades). Fabulous!

The \u201cCritical Hit\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the \u2018Critical Backer\u2019 icon for your name on the website (wherever you see your name, in forums, profile, scoreboards etc. there\u2019ll be a little \u2018Critical Backer\u2019 icon next to it, so everyone knows how fantastic, generous and just plain cool you are) // + 66 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades). Fantastic!

The \u201cMurder Temperature\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the prefix of \u201cBadboy" (or "-girl\u201d) for your username on the website // nominate a song to be used as an achievement in the game! // + 92 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades).  Sweet!

The \u201cTriple Positive\u201d tier - all previous rewards + your name in lights in the \u2018Extra Special Thanks\u2019 part of the credits on the actual game! // the suffix of \u201cthe Positive\u201d for your username on the website // + a Kickstarter exclusive, Special Edition \u2018Backer\u2019 t-shirt (choose from 3 designs) // and 111 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades)!

The \u201cMagnum\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the prefix of \u201cSpecial\u201d or \u201cDirty\u201d for your username on the website // two Special Edition \u2018Backer\u2019 t-shirts (choose from 3 designs) // an exclusive .pdf of concept art and background information from the development of the game // + 357 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades). Wahoo!

The \u201cNeighbor of the Beast\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the suffix of \u201cActual\u201d on the website // all three special edition \u2018Backer\u2019 t-shirts // +667 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades).  Holy Moly!

The \u201cElite\u201d tier - all previous rewards +  the prefix of \u201cLeet\u201d for your username on the website // + a competition run in your name, for a song of your choice // + 1337 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades).  The world would be a better place with more people like you in it!

The \u201cCountdown\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the prefix or suffix of "King" (or "Queen") for your name on the website // PLUS contribute to the creation of a custom background featured in the game! // + 4321 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades). AND a free copy of every future Freq. game we make. - If this doesn't make you feel good you must be dead inside.  :-)

The \u201cThere can be only one\u201d tier - all previous rewards + the title of \u201cEmperor\u201d prefixed to your username on the website // Name an upgrade! (i.e. Bill\u2019s BFG) that all players can buy with Freq. Bucks! // + 5000 Freq.Bucks (to spend on in-game upgrades) // PLUS a free copy of every future Freq. game we make on every platform! // AND dinner with the Directors for you and one guest (which if you\u2019ve seen the way we eat, may not be such a good thing!).  General fame and adulation!  :-)
